#                                          #
############################################

1.  Includes
      - main.py
      - MtGox.py
      - DataSet.py
      - Data.py

2.  New Features
      - Mean, standard deviation, and fitted slope calculations
        for buy, sell, last, volume, high, and low values
      - Nice table display with values
      - User-chosen time frame over which to calculate values

3.  Setup
      - Change USERNAME and PASSWORD values in MtGox.py (NECESSARY)
      - Change BUY_THRESHOLD, SELL_THRESHOLD, and UPDATE_TIME values
        in main.py (not necessary, but recommended)
      - Change DEFAULT_SIMULATION value in MtGox.py (change at your
        own risk... this is still in pre-alpha state)

4.  Run Command
      - python main.py

5.  Question, Comments, Bug Fixes?
      - http://www.reddit.com/r/redbit

6.  Updates
      - https://github.com/hyppo/Redbit

